==== POS-Tech 1.1.3 ====

== Installation and database configuration ==

-- Requirements --

POS-Tech requires Java 1.6 and corresponding database connector. Derby connector
is provided in the lib directory.

-- Installation procedure --

To install POS-Tech just copy the entire directory where you want. By default
it will use a derby database in your home directory.

Run configure.sh or configure.bat to change the configuration. Supported
databases are Derby, MySQL and PostgreSQL.

== Other documentation ==

Check http://trac.scil.coop/pos-tech for further information.

